asset_contract.name: FLUF
asset_contract.description:
This is FLUF World…

A metaverse ecosystem of NFT character collectables and a global, creative community. From our genesis collection Flufs, to Thingies, Party Bears and more to come, we’re building a world that’s yours to shape, explore and call home. 

Flufs are the collection that started it all. 10,000 3D rabbit avatars, programmatically-generated from over 270 traits! Unique by at least three degrees of separation, Flufs are yours to trade, collect and customise through our growing Scenes & Sounds collection. 

But Flufs aren’t just furry faces... Metaverse-ready and full of surprises, they’re your ticket to a world of exclusive content, digital connectivity, IRL experiences and more.

Welcome to the Fluffle. 

---

**Official Collections:**

[FLUF World: Thingies](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-thingies)

[FLUF World: Burrows](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-burrows)

[FLUF World: Scenes & Sounds](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-scenes-and-sounds)

A metaverse ecosystem of NFT character collectables and a global, creative community. From our genesis collection Flufs, to Thingies, Party Bears and more to come, we’re building a world that’s yours to shape, explore and call home. 

Flufs are the collection that started it all. 10,000 3D rabbit avatars, programmatically-generated from over 270 traits! Unique by at least three degrees of separation, Flufs are yours to trade, collect and customise through our growing Scenes & Sounds collection. 

But Flufs aren’t just furry faces... Metaverse-ready and full of surprises, they’re your ticket to a world of exclusive content, digital connectivity, IRL experiences and more.

Welcome to the Fluffle.

description: Born into the likes of money most Fluffs have never dreamed about, Baller has never wanted for anything in life except acceptance and happiness. With a moody blue demeanor by nature, he has been working on finding the positives in his lavish existence for a number of years now with limited success. Extreme wealth has meant he never really had to commit fully to anything, his hobbies tend to change with the seasons and whatever is hopping in celebrity circles around Bunnerly Hills in FluffyWood, the snooty end of the underground he has the privilege of calling home. A series of semi famous girlfriends including Marilyn Bunroe and Jennifur Bunniston aside, his love life has been lack lustre to say the least. Recently the hip hop scene has been bouncing and surprise surprise, true to form, Baller has suddenly acquired gold chains, gold hoops and a blue lambo to boot. Perhaps these new shiny accessories will attract love? The wrong side of 30, he is really looking forward to meeting his dream Fluffette. That seems to be the only thing this bunny has not been able to find a price tag on. As suming the new bling and rev machine work in his pursuit, Baller is dearly hoping it will also be a chance to say bye bye to the high pressure he feels, and hello to happily ever. A mansion full of flufflets does sound tiring, thankfully the help will attend to them! Its tough at the top.

asset_contract.description:
This is FLUF World…

A metaverse ecosystem of NFT character collectables and a global, creative community. From our genesis collection Flufs, to Thingies, Party Bears and more to come, we’re building a world that’s yours to shape, explore and call home. 

Flufs are the collection that started it all. 10,000 3D rabbit avatars, programmatically-generated from over 270 traits! Unique by at least three degrees of separation, Flufs are yours to trade, collect and customise through our growing Scenes & Sounds collection. 

But Flufs aren’t just furry faces... Metaverse-ready and full of surprises, they’re your ticket to a world of exclusive content, digital connectivity, IRL experiences and more.

Welcome to the Fluffle.

A metaverse ecosystem of NFT character collectables and a global, creative community. From our genesis collection Flufs, to Thingies, Party Bears and more to come, we’re building a world that’s yours to shape, explore and call home. 

Flufs are the collection that started it all. 10,000 3D rabbit avatars, programmatically-generated from over 270 traits! Unique by at least three degrees of separation, Flufs are yours to trade, collect and customise through our growing Scenes & Sounds collection. 

But Flufs aren’t just furry faces... Metaverse-ready and full of surprises, they’re your ticket to a world of exclusive content, digital connectivity, IRL experiences and more.

Welcome to the Fluffle.

I mean come this Fluf is literally shaking with red fricking lazer beams coming out his eyeballs.
